oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Magnolia Camp #51
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of a Workmen of the World graveyard ceremony. The group is Magnolia Camp #51 from Humboldt, Tennessee. Men, women, and children are gathered around a headstone with the group's banner hanging above.
